<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Certificado de Vacunaci√≥n - <%= @vaccination.pet.name %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background: white;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #4F46E5;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #4F46E5;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .certificate-body {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .section {
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .section-content {
      color: #111827;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-item {
      padding: 10px;
      background: #F9FAFB;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6B7280;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .info-value {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #111827;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 2px solid #E5E7EB;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6B7280;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .signature-section {
      margin-top: 60px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .signature-box {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .signature-line {
      border-top: 2px solid #111827;
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }
    @media print {
      body { padding: 20px; }
      .no-print { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>üêæ CERTIFICADO DE VACUNACI√ìN</h1>
    <p style="color: #6B7280; margin-top: 10px;">VetConnect - Sistema de Gesti√≥n Veterinaria</p>
  </div>

  <div class="certificate-body">
    <div class="section">
      <p class="section-content" style="text-align: justify;">
        Por medio del presente documento se certifica que la mascota mencionada a continuaci√≥n 
        ha recibido la vacunaci√≥n especificada en las condiciones y fechas indicadas.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-item">
        <div class="info-label">Mascota</div>
        <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.pet.name %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <div class="info-label">Especie</div>
        <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.pet.species.humanize %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <div class="info-label">Raza</div>
        <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.pet.breed || 'N/A' %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <div class="info-label">Due√±o</div>
        <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.pet.user.full_name %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">Informaci√≥n de la Vacunaci√≥n</div>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">Vacuna</div>
          <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.vaccine_name %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">Tipo</div>
          <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.vaccine_type.humanize %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">Fecha de Administraci√≥n</div>
          <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.administered_at.strftime('%d de %B de %Y') %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <div class="info-label">Dosis N√∫mero</div>
          <div class="info-value">#<%= @vaccination.dose_number %></div>
        </div>
        <% if @vaccination.manufacturer.present? %>
          <div class="info-item">
            <div class="info-label">Fabricante</div>
            <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.manufacturer %></div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        <% if @vaccination.lot_number.present? %>
          <div class="info-item">
            <div class="info-label">N√∫mero de Lote</div>
            <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.lot_number %></div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        <% if @vaccination.next_due_date.present? %>
          <div class="info-item">
            <div class="info-label">Pr√≥xima Dosis</div>
            <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.next_due_date.strftime('%d de %B de %Y') %></div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if @vaccination.notes.present? %>
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Observaciones</div>
        <div class="section-content"><%= simple_format(@vaccination.notes) %></div>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <div class="signature-section">
      <div class="signature-box">
        <div class="signature-line">
          <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.veterinarian.full_name %></div>
          <div class="info-label">Veterinario</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="signature-box">
        <div class="signature-line">
          <div class="info-value"><%= @vaccination.administered_at.strftime('%d/%m/%Y') %></div>
          <div class="info-label">Fecha</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Este certificado fue generado electr√≥nicamente por VetConnect</p>
    <p>ID de Vacunaci√≥n: #<%= @vaccination.id %> | Generado el <%= Time.current.strftime('%d/%m/%Y a las %H:%M') %></p>
    <div class="no-print" style="margin-top: 20px;">
      <%= link_to '‚Üê Volver a la vacunaci√≥n', vaccination_path(@vaccination), 
          style: "color: #4F46E5; text-decoration: none;" %>
      | 
      <a href="javascript:window.print()" style="color: #4F46E5; text-decoration: none;">üñ®Ô∏è Imprimir</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
